Package apollo.dataadapter.chado

Class Summary
ChadoAdapter A data adapter that allows Apollo to communicate with a Chado-compliant relational database.
ChadoAdapterGUI In the Apollo data adapter specification each data adapter has two parts: a class that implements the graphical user interface, and a class that interacts with the data source (as directed by the user via the GUI).
ChadoAdHocFlatFileWriter Writes a curation set to an ad-hoc chado-based flat file format.
ChadoDatabase Connection and configuration information for a Chado database.
ChadoTransaction Class that represents the chado XML counterpart of an Apollo transaction.
ChadoTransaction.Operation INNER CLASS Operation
ChadoTransactionTransformer This class is used to translate Apollo Transaction objects to Chado Transaction objects.
